    <item>
      <title>当特朗普接受加密议程时，数字资产立法被推动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/digital-asset-legislation-pushed-as-trump-embraces-crypto-agenda</link>
      <description><![CDATA[代表拜伦·唐纳德（Byron Donalds）将于周五提出立法，以编纂唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统本月初签署的行政命令，该命令建立了战略性比特币储备和美国数字资产库存。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/digital-asset-legislation-pushed-as-trump-embraces-crypto-agenda</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Mar 2025 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
