    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟国家支持俄罗斯大亨制裁的扩展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/eu-poised-to-back-extension-of-sanctions-on-russian-tycoons</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在匈牙利放弃反对派之后，欧盟成员国同意扩大对包括许多亿万富翁在内的单个俄罗斯人的制裁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/eu-poised-to-back-extension-of-sanctions-on-russian-tycoons</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Mar 2025 19:14:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>超过一半的英国机柜敦促里夫斯重新考虑支出削减</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/over-half-of-uk-cabinet-urges-reeves-to-rethink-spending-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理凯尔·斯塔默（Keir Starmer）的内阁中有一半以上敦促他的校长瑞秋·里夫斯（Rachel Reeves）重新考虑她的计划，以缩减福利和支出，这是一个非常关心的工党在迫在眉睫的削减范围内越来越关注的迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/over-half-of-uk-cabinet-urges-reeves-to-rethink-spending-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Mar 2025 18:12:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
